OL,3,CPeople urged to share views on how to
OL,4,Cclean up water and rebuild trust
OL,6,FThe water industry's problems are not
OL,7,Fthe "inevitable consequence" of
OL,8,Fprivatisation, the chairman of a
OL,9,Fcommission set up to examine reforms
OL,10,Fof the sector has said.
OL,12,FThe Government-appointed Independent
OL,13,FWater Commission is launching its call
OL,14,Ffor evidence on Thursday, asking the
OL,15,Fpublic, environmental groups,
OL,16,Finvestors and others their views on
OL,17,Freform of the troubled sector.
