OL,3,CPeople urged to share views on how to
OL,4,Cclean up water and rebuild trust
OL,6,FThey are being urged to share their
OL,7,Fviews on how to secure the
OL,8,F"significant" prize of cleaner waters,
OL,9,Fgrowth, and a stable, well-funded
OL,10,Fwater sector for future generations.
OL,12,FThe launch comes amid ongoing public
OL,13,Fanger over the degraded and polluted
OL,14,Fstate of the country's rivers, lakes
OL,15,Fand coasts, soaring water bills and
OL,16,Fprivatised water companies' dividends,
OL,17,Fdebt and executive bonuses.
