OL,3,CPeople urged to share views on how to
OL,4,Cclean up water and rebuild trust
OL,6,FThe commission is looking for views on
OL,7,Fthe strategic management of water, the
OL,8,Fregulatory system, including economic,
OL,9,Fenvironmental and drinking water
OL,10,Fregulation, water company ownership
OL,11,Fmodels, and improving the resilience
OL,12,Fof assets from pipes to reservoirs, as
OL,13,Fwell as supply chains.
OL,15,FFormer deputy governor of the Bank of
OL,16,FEngland Sir Jon Cunliffe, who is
OL,17,Fchairing the commission, said its
OL,18,Finitial work since it was announced in
OL,19,FOctober 2024 has highlighted a range
OL,20,Fof serious and often interlocking
OL,21,Fconcerns.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
