OL,3,CPeople urged to share views on how to
OL,4,Cclean up water and rebuild trust
OL,6,F"Ambitious changes will be needed to
OL,7,Faddress these concerns and rebuild the
OL,8,Ftrust in the system that has broken
OL,9,Fdown on all sides ` customers,
OL,10,Fenvironmental groups, investors and
OL,11,Fcompanies.
OL,13,F"The problems we see today have not
OL,14,Femerged overnight. Nor, do I believe,
OL,15,Fare they the inevitable consequence of
OL,16,Fa privatise regulated company model,"
OL,17,Fhe said.
