OL,3,CPeople urged to share views on how to
OL,4,Cclean up water and rebuild trust
OL,6,F"Rather, they have developed over time
OL,7,Fand due to factors including poor
OL,8,Fdecisions and poor performance by
OL,9,Fcompanies, regulatory gaps, policy
OL,10,Finstability and a history of ad-hoc
OL,11,Fchanges that have left an increasingly
OL,12,Fcomplex system that is no longer
OL,13,Fworking well for anyone," he added.
OL,15,F"Our task is to stand back from the
OL,16,Fcurrent system and explore, with an
OL,17,Fopen mind, potential changes."
