OL,3,CPeople urged to share views on how to
OL,4,Cclean up water and rebuild trust
OL,6,FHe added: "We should not forget that
OL,7,Fthe prize here is significant `
OL,8,Fcleaner waters, growth and a stable,
OL,9,Fwell-funded sector that can deliver
OL,10,Fessential, world-class services for
OL,11,Ffuture generations."
OL,13,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said:
OL,14,F"Our waterways are polluted and our
OL,15,Fwater system urgently needs fixing.
OL,17,F"Earlier this week our ground-breaking
OL,18,FWater Act became law, with new powers
OL,19,Fto ban the payment of unfair bonuses
OL,20,Ffor polluting water bosses and bring
OL,21,Fcriminal charges against lawbreakers.
