OL,6,FCommenting on the launch of the Water
OL,7,FCommission's call for evidence, the
OL,8,Fchairman of the Environment, Food and
OL,9,FRural Affairs Committee, Alistair
OL,10,FCarmichael, whose committee is
OL,11,Finvestigating the problems in the
OL,12,Findustry, said: "There is huge public
OL,13,Fconcern about the performance of water
OL,14,Fcompanies amidst repeated incidents of
OL,15,Fwater outages, sewage pollution and
OL,16,Foutbreaks of contamination in domestic
OL,17,Fwater supplies.
